The countries and overseas territories/communities that have newly
reported their first pandemic (H1N1) 2009 confirmed cases since the
last web update (No. 110): none.

The countries and overseas territories/communities that have newly
reported their first deaths among pandemic (H1N1) 2009 confirmed cases
since the last web update (No. 110): none.

Region / Deaths*
----------------
